verses.verse: Praise <WH1984> ye Jehovah <WH3050>. Praise <WH1984>, O ye servants <WH5650> of Jehovah <WH3050>, Praise <WH1984> the name <WH8034> of Jehovah <WH3068>.
Blessed <WH1288> be the name <WH8034> of Jehovah <WH3068> From this time forth <WH6258> and for <WH5704> evermore <WH5769>.
From the rising <WH4217> of the sun <WH8121> unto the going down <WH3996> of the same Jehovah <WH3068>'s name <WH8034> is to be praised <WH1984>.
Jehovah <WH3068> is high <WH7311> above <WH7311> all nations <WH1471>, And his glory <WH3519> above <WH7311> the heavens <WH8064>.
Who is like unto Jehovah <WH3068> our God <WH430>, That hath his seat <WH3427> on high <WH1361>,
That humbleth <WH8213> himself to behold <WH7200> The things that are in heaven <WH8064> and in the earth <WH776>?
He raiseth up <WH6965> the poor <WH1800> out of the dust <WH6083>, And lifteth <WH7311> up the needy <WH34> from the dunghill <WH830>;
That he may set <WH3427> him with princes <WH5081>, Even with the princes <WH5081> of his people <WH5971>.
He maketh the barren woman <WH6135> to keep <WH3427> house <WH1004>, And to be a joyful <WH8056> mother <WH517> of children <WH1121>. Praise <WH1984> ye Jehovah <WH3050>.
